Package github.lightningcreations.lcjei.resources

Package for interfaces related to resource binding.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Resource<ResourceKey>
    Represents a Raw object somewhere which can be read and is named by a ResourceKey.
    ResourceKeyMapper<GuestKeyType,HostKeyType>
    Represents a bi-directional function between the keys of a Host resource set and a Guest resource set.
    This interface defines a strict contract that ResourceKeyMapper.mapToGuest(Object) and ResourceKeyMapper.mapToHost(Object) must be inverse operations.
    ResourceSet<ResourceKey>
    Represents a Set of Resources in some unspecified repository.
    The ResourceSet is guaranteed to reflect the state of the underlying repository at creation type and after each reload.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MappedResourceSet<GuestKeyType,HostKeyType>
    Defines a set of resources mapped from one key type, to annother.
